TODO: Create a wifi process module that will act as a state machine to handle connection and ip get events, this state machine will react to 
events from wifi middleware and perform the associated process


stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> INIT
    INIT --> GET_CREDENTIALS
    GET_CREDENTIALS --> CONNECT : Found Credentials
    GET_CREDENTIALS --> ENABLE_WIFI_CONFIG_MODE : No Credentials
    CONNECT --> WAIT_CONNECT
    WAIT_CONNECT --> CONNECT : Fail to connect && trys < MAX_TRYS
    WAIT_CONNECT --> WAIT_GET_IP : Sucess
    WAIT_CONNECT --> ENABLE_WIFI_CONFIG_MODE : Max trys reached
    WAIT_GET_IP --> CONNECT : IP Timeout
    WAIT_GET_IP --> [*] : Got IP